    "Title": "Silence Sentries",
    "Description": "Our resistance movement is growing by the day, but that comes with some unwanted attention.  Recent scans discovered orbital sentries at ~mission(location|address) and a ship running a patrol pattern. We believe this is part of an espionage campaign targeting XenoThreat, most likely funded by the UEE. \n\nWe\u2019re looking for an experienced merc willing to destroy the sentries ASAP.  Since they already have eyes and ears on us, sending in someone from outside the org would draw less attention. If you take the gig, you\u2019ll be paid promptly once the sentries are destroyed.\n \nNow, while the patrol ship isn\u2019t the main target, we suspect that if it escapes it might have reinforcements in reserve. Might be smart to deal with it promptly. \n\nIf you decide to help us, XenoThreat will remember you\u2019re someone willing to fight for what\u2019s right.\n\nComm. Spec. Engler",
